					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Managing one's time really is an important topic. I have maybe 4 to 8 hours a week to work on my homebrew. And the one thing that keeps me moving forward is a rather granular TODO list. I plan out all the next things to do, as  well as the bugs I need to squash. Also internal versioning helps as well. 
<br />
<br />Does anyone do anything similar?</div>

